    <3>1. UNCHANGED <<maxVBal, maxVVal>>
      BY DEF vars
    <3>2. UNCHANGED PmaxBal
      BY DEF vars, PmaxBal, 1bOr2bMsgs
    <3>3. UNCHANGED msgs
