            BY <4>2, <5>2, mm.acc = a  \* <7>3
          <6>2. ASSUME NEW mm \in mA(a)
                PROVE  mm \in mA(a)'
             BY <4>2
          <6>3. QED
            BY <6>1, <6>2
        <5>4. QED
          BY <5>3

      <4>8. PmaxBal' = [PmaxBal EXCEPT ![self] = b]
        <5>1. SUFFICES ASSUME  NEW a \in Acceptor
                       PROVE    PmaxBal'[a] = IF a = self THEN b
